node.text:
took my mom to see @usher perform in Vegas for his residency friends & fam opening night. The show was sooo good. I knew every single song lol we was singing to the top of our lungs. 😭😌
Fun fact: Usher & Janet Jackson was the first concert my mom took me to as a kid. 🙂 if you haven’t been, it’s a must see, take a quick trip to Vegas ✨⚡️ thank you for everything @boogsneffect i love u 💖🤰🏻
[ for: hb site. Link in bio ]
